  <listitem><para><xref linkend="TuneXAutoTicks" /></para></listitem>
  <listitem><para><xref linkend="TuneYAutoTicks" /></para></listitem>
</itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect1>

<sect1 id="ref-scaling">
<title>Scaling and Translation</title>
<para>
The functions in this section control the overall data scaling and
positioning of the plot on the image, or translate coordinates.
</para>

<para>
<itemizedlist>
  <listitem><para><xref linkend="GetDeviceXY" /></para></listitem>
  <listitem><para><xref linkend="SetMarginsPixels" /></para></listitem>
  <listitem><para><xref linkend="SetPieAutoSize" /></para></listitem>
