</para>
</sect1>

<sect1 id="ref-callbacks">
<title>Callbacks</title>
<para>
The functions in this section are used to implement callbacks.
This is an advanced feature described in more detail in
<xref linkend="callbacks"/>.
</para>

<para>
<itemizedlist>
  <listitem><para><xref linkend="GetCallback"/></para></listitem>
  <listitem><para><xref linkend="RemoveCallback"/></para></listitem>
  <listitem><para><xref linkend="SetCallback"/></para></listitem>
</itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect1>


